lead_paragraph: When six of nine scholarship players score in double figures and three register double-doubles, even hard-to-please Syracuse coach Jim Boeheim can find a few reasons to smile.

headline.print_headline: No. 18 Syracuse Holds SC State to 27 Percent in 101-59 Rout
